Title: Windows Managed Interface
Description: Contains all windows native API, classes, interfaces, structures, enumerations, constant to use through dot net languages.

Project Description
Contains all windows classes, interfaces, structs, enums, constant to use through dot net languages.

This Project aim to import entire msdn into managed code to make it easy to use native windows element through dot net languages.
